Behavior:
- WAIT for element to be available inside DOM
- Use one namespace only: window.MTKHierarchy.

Restrictions:
- No frameworks.
- No jQuery.
- No Bootstrap JavaScript.
- No external libraries.
- ADA compliant CODE

Accessibility:
- Use semantic HTML.
- Keyboard accessible.
- Visible focus states.
- ADA compliant

